        "content": "<p>Can someone explain to me why this is not working. I'm really new to register_labell_attr:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Lean.LabelAttribute</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\">/-</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  test label</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">-/</span>\n<span class=\"n\">register_label_attr</span> <span class=\"n\">rom</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">@[</span><span class=\"n\">rom</span><span class=\"kd\">]</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- unknown attribute rom</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">womp</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">4</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">rfl</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
